OL,3,CHealth trusts asked to draw up cost
OL,4,Csavings to cover #300m budget shortfall
OL,6,FHealth trusts in Northern Ireland have
OL,7,Fbeen asked to work up cost-saving
OL,8,Fplans as part of efforts to bridge an
OL,9,Festimated #300 million budget gap.
OL,11,FIt is understood the plans are due to
OL,12,Fbe delivered to the Department of
OL,13,FHealth by the end of May, at which
OL,14,Fpoint Health Minister Robin Swann will
OL,15,Fbe required to make decisions on how
OL,16,Fto reduce spending.
OL,18,FA benchmarking exercise conducted by
OL,19,Fexperts working with NHS England is
OL,20,Falready under way to identify other
OL,21,Fpotential savings.
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G1/8
