OL,3,CHealth trusts asked to draw up cost
OL,4,Csavings to cover #300m budget shortfall
OL,6,FThe minister had bid for an additional
OL,7,F#1 billion ` an amount that
OL,8,Frepresented the entirety of the
OL,9,Funcommitted funding available for
OL,10,Fdistribution among all Stormont
OL,11,Fdepartments.
OL,13,FThe #1 billion comprised #300 million
OL,14,Fto maintain a pay award made to health
OL,15,Fstaff at the end of the last financial
OL,16,Fyear as part of the Government's
OL,17,Ffinancial package to restore
OL,18,Fpowersharing. It also included #150
OL,19,Fmillion to make a further 3% pay award
OL,20,Fto staff in this financial year.
