OL,3,CHealth trusts asked to draw up cost
OL,4,Csavings to cover #300m budget shortfall
OL,6,FAmong the allocations within that #550
OL,7,Fmillion was #200 million to cover
OL,8,Fprojected overspends by the five main
OL,9,Fhealth trusts (the trusts overspent by
OL,10,F#150 million last year); #80 million
OL,11,Fto reduce red flag cancer waiting
OL,12,Flists; #70 million to account for
OL,13,Finflation; #70 million to cover the
OL,14,Fcosts of new drugs expected to become
OL,15,Favailable in 2024/25; and #80 million
OL,16,Fto pay for the impact of the UK
OL,17,FGovernment rise in the national
OL,18,Fminimum wage.
