OL,3,CHealth trusts asked to draw up cost
OL,4,Csavings to cover #300m budget shortfall
OL,6,FMr Swann had told Executive colleagues
OL,7,Fhe was prepared to accept an
OL,8,Fadditional #800 million in the budget
OL,9,Fand would look to make up the #200
OL,10,Fmillion shortfall on the #1 billion
OL,11,Fwith in-year reallocations from
OL,12,Fcentral funds and potential cost-
OL,13,Fsaving steps such as limiting the 2024/
OL,14,F25 pay award to 2%.
OL,16,FHowever, he said the #500 million he
OL,17,Fhas been allocated by the Executive is
OL,18,Funsustainable and will have serious
OL,19,Fconsequences for health service
OL,20,Fdelivery in Northern Ireland.
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G6/8
