OL,3,CHealth trusts asked to draw up cost
OL,4,Csavings to cover #300m budget shortfall
OL,6,FMr Swann has also been allocated #34
OL,7,Fmillion as part of the UK Government's
OL,8,Ffinancial deal for specific
OL,9,Finitiatives to tackle the region's
OL,10,Fspiralling waiting lists.
OL,12,FOfficials in Mr Swann's department are
OL,13,Fnow examining how the estimated #300
OL,14,Fmillion hole in their spending plans
OL,15,Fcan be plugged, with the health
OL,16,Ftrusts' plans central to shaping
OL,17,Ffuture ministerial decisions on future
OL,18,Fservice provision in Northern Ireland.
